Class BasicNeuralDataSet

java.lang.Object
  org.encog.neural.data.basic.BasicNeuralDataSet
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Iterable<NeuralDataPair>, EngineDataSet, EngineIndexableSet, Indexable, NeuralDataSet, EncogPersistedObject
Direct Known Subclasses:
ImageNeuralDataSet, TemporalNeuralDataSet
public class BasicNeuralDataSet
extends java.lang.Object
implements EncogPersistedObject, java.io.Serializable, Indexable

neural data in an ArrayList. This class is memory based, so large enough datasets could cause memory issues. Many other dataset types extend this class.

Author:
jheaton
